snippet.title: Gaming Indoors
snippet.description:
Hi YouTube, I'm Ali. Welcome to my channel!

As well as playing and reviewing all kinds of  table-top, roleplaying, board, card and dice games, I'll be getting to grips with the underlying mechanics of modern board games, learning to paint and 3d print my own miniatures, investigating what it takes to design and publish a game, discovering the history behind some of favorite handheld console games and generally doing things a grown man should have stopped doing years ago.

Oh .. And I'll probably play some video games too.

Thanks for watching, welcome to Gaming Indoors!

snippet.title: Noobs Gaming Alpha
snippet.description:
Welcome to the official YouTube Channel for Noobs Gaming 

Hello! I'm Meninx_NMBT and this is the Noobs Gaming Channel.

We are a group of gamers that is made up of friends and family. 

We have been playing video games for a long time from in the 80s with the Atari, spectrum, Sega MS/MD and onto the Nintendo and then PlayStation, until we moved to PC gaming with Counter Strike and TFC, then the newer consoles like the Xbox and PlayStation, we then moved to PC again for Star Citizen.

We play many games, and you may see other games pop up on here from our members, such as GTA, WoW, Destiny, COD and F1, but our main content will be Star Citizen as we have just got into this game and are building a crew

We hope you like the channel and become part of our Noob Gaming Family:-
Meninx, Kilthanis, JackyBoy

snippet.title: Three Minute Gaming
snippet.description:
Game reviews don't need to be long. Here we make high quality reviews that respect your time while still letting you know if a game is worth checking out. So you'll have more time to get back to gaming and less time watching somebody reviewing.

Primary focus is on Game Pass / PS+ releases but also focus on AAA and indie games.

...but the truth is I just play a bunch of games and review what I'm playing. Hopefully I can help you find some good ones. 

Please be polite and respectful to others and their opinions. I'm always curious to hear your opinions on games and the reviews, so please feel free to leave a comment! 

For media inquiries/review codes, etc. please contact me either via Email or Twitter.

snippet.title: Cloud Gaming Xtreme
snippet.description:
We love to cover every Cloud Gaming Platform with comparisons, reviews, gameplay videos and news updates as they happen so you can choose the right platform for you. 
We cover the following platforms regularly:
Nvidia Geforce Now
Xbox Cloud Gaming (Xcloud)
Shadow PC
Google Stadia
Amazon Luna

We also love to try new systems like VectorDash, Boosteroid and PlayNware and are always looking for new ones to test. 

Join us on Social as well for discussions outside of youtube:
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/cloudgamingxtreme

Discord: https://rebrand.ly/vjukydo
